; line-height: 1.4;"&gt;《山色苍白》&lt;/em&gt;剧照，由广濑铃（左）和二阶堂富美主演。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;来源：Vue Lumière&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;对话开始者&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;击败一个政权比取代一个政权更容易。&lt;/strong&gt;伊拉克战争表明，推翻政府可能会引发&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/lBDmsM7DgAJKkqjoBosphl891nEpe79SraAxr6zsdRcu5YVxUvSgNP1L1Rjr65LwiKdEvp3tUSzwnx4xGPN6JOnao23k04gZUvK7JBlsfDqJslvm1l1ycdKhv2maW1rm08GdunBKAtr3F1X2-ALaMCnQdfyrCrl-MikpMbPXdd45M5kDDW0HwjlrVDD11I6Zp27aWydJX1yRQry1I2wJjEQ_oFxpunR4PFTXa-ZXZ15Fz5p8b5v2GzSnjodLfIZfibqJjr4loJaUM0c28OX3Y6DqiuqP_bEdDm17o_LdRHykFkey3YtXE3s3-33ujlD-vvm4Sa7Zuc4TstAfjgD0g_KJioRrwbfEF1rMIImI41-9-QPfZzDCQY9v9mFx1ubvKeRiY3KnZglexIvddiRkWNF8fLa-TPZ-AF3e1Y2SHV9nFCuCgskvINySWdaWC9u7cB7igW4JoGXBuLGgCpBOXUDuaQPDIHbdBdlnPhAZUXEuHgN8BEQviS5JZP2yTDk-FKCbJjUp3LDGq6bKvfWsXKJ2GNbPW02uxcPUUA/HRI8LNYU22vVMDjfezdpk2w9r78iyGDu/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊拉克战争告诉我们有关伊朗冲突的信息"&gt;更难以控制的&lt;/a&gt;不稳定局势。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;印度的企业集团正在阻碍这一进程。&lt;/strong&gt;它们的扩张&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/gL7MhVNfgsw2aaVkdwf237UzRyJip5Wc_hI_kH3PTy94QZyJkk3rwiXC0Lu6yl-WQnr-WOMyR0AuqRukU0sQjIaiSbo5EWQLYfcPjoCmx_AtVbIDNsPRdv9Q_8TiO-qPEIMJxvuHvUeqEUeM2UO0JDG5KzfhI5L-4U5MhRvr9WKSyxR4SR7XT0lU-eJep7HqFkbe-Ug6o_Lac5qfyNyjWMTY1oUK_FnSjofcBAEMUU6b_RCDjtK8j4duvREQ9Tw_Sbb1H1dkjVAC5zcqoNG3ZRmDBUcE-C__NhWtsvxyZS_j6A-Y70S7njlZvnra_Z4m-uBU4gBQUQgr4qnGJNKfj_9yHhoigy_XadiQL9RLLXUkPLmH1mhzz5r6ehYM3S4Lgt69XlksmWFr5XJtVJlVcHYrPyg8Nl-7limrw1qoDToNvnkw031ee7NbenLCQlMHLdWAXpn