20px !important;"&gt;为什么战争结束后天然气价格仍将保持高位&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;在本周&lt;em style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;"&gt;《彭博商业周刊》的《大家都忙》&lt;/em&gt;节目中，我们解释了伊朗战争对供应链造成的损害如何意味着全美价格将在更长时间内上涨。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;一名联邦法官猛烈抨击特朗普政府&lt;/strong&gt;试图对美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔(Jerome Powell)展开刑事调查， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/jZCV0shY-JK2nmHEdl60R9Ke23XdKwH5OyH0XWHZMCPlxPD-i18oA5BmgchYoArJ7yokVqyD_XNP__MfojUvywZcXEZsfrSs1Xcn9M357aElKVF7nkJY_q_2-t0rRPFEOpZBkEMdCjOijukkWVRIJGVsJ7TXONiQ4QOyzRaLjYklUY3XRQIjRI_KGUQmxUnQtbvAhtocD5nqzlgZJrXxpCvZQ5Y-gX9pVaaKYNTBq06gLoLbaaJwh7AYHvv82R35G6nQFmWPwUoLzac-JN4xykR4z8cqnDXPIUvEI0pFqVdwxTvuikQfMzMEDvCT4BA1BzQ886L67JEtgXkhJbBgSZLYmN4T/_tlhhEQ8YgJPenZDyGK4l3k9pTY3hb81/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="联邦法官撤销司法部对美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的传票美国有线电视新闻网政治"&gt;并拒绝了司法部最近一次失败的传票，&lt;/a&gt;司法部&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/vfuJnmWx3wg4URUqclBIfJKltjAD1az42P9sDI1-W3BkHqIBoe5aPxcxvX1HtMb34VUznZeo-mNEjIm4EzNA4wuKKZowJkeFZZclaiT9q_rtV917hapWVdYQtCIjuKVX0ZkGuz1i766ySiJX6iEV7Kjzna5KEt5D-K_SRvXbYgomXd1NOXSeiMRpB9p1S82Xsamjt5j7iwRhHAJ-OiLOzd2NT3wbULSAw0TW0IkYLgzo8GLUxuab0RsDfvYDgrsciU-jLXhSQU1Q_5TZEoVxV1EQ-_yprb93kZNmwu4nH36jYa7mmq2RiFirKwsO2QqBw4w081sC5B1xePaLrahnVrFXpc67Hc-B87P6vDjFWzcQDIUwvdaJ2NLRM9Q9RDA0zuSh-bZ3JthlbpxabQ38qTFH59VVhNwcGFT2n5aRY8R8Gpgy2NiW0l3K1QjJ-1QozHbg8oMkmDlhhRbagqtS66ogshcz3xdxHxomJMjub6N-Xubyj0VVx5jwEOvH3ZqSHO1wzmwk/jpP_YhycuFQANcPGtlN3gqPiQPKNwAYz/18" rel="noope